e offices, the AutoFull M6 is quickly becoming the preferred choice for anyone needing an ergonomic chair that supports long hours of sitting with exceptional comfort and durability.<\/p>","link_url":"","link_text":"","link_style":"link"}}},"block_order":["item_kP8Bdp","item_9d9hy3","item_PREWfY"],"settings":{"section_id":"","full_width":true,"stack_on_mobile":false,"gap":"medium","text_alignment":"start","subheading":"","title":"","content":"","background":"#ffffff","background_gradient":"","text_color":"","padding_top":64,"padding_bottom":64,"padding_top_mob":48,"padding_bottom_mob":48}},"rich_text_bYj7BH":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"subheading_gdhnPF":{"type":"subheading","settings":{"text":"FEATURES"}},"heading_cAxyH7":{"type":"heading","settings":{"text":"A4 Pro Gaming Desk","heading_tag":"h1","font_style":"normal","custom_size":102,"text_color":"","gradient":"","allow_gradient_v2":true,"gradient_v2":""}},"richtext_tkpNEr":{"type":"richtext","settings":{"content":"<p>Switch seamlessly between sitting (28\") and standing (48\") to crush sedentary stiffness. With a wide 20-inch height range, the autofull A4 Pro gaming desk adapts to any body type—no hunching, no straining. Engineered for marathon gamers who won’t let discomfort break their focus.<\/p>","custom_width":false,"content_width_p":"medium"}}},"block_order":["subheading_gdhnPF","heading_cAxyH7","richtext_tkpNEr"],"settings":{"section_id":"","linked_to":false,"full_width":true,"content_width":"medium","text_position":"center","text_position_mob":"center","background":"#f6f6f6","background_gradient":"","text_color":"","padding_top":64,"padding_bottom":64,"padding_top_mob":48,"padding_bottom_mob":48}},"media_with_text_iDMn7m":{"type":"media-with-text","blocks":{"image_E8QdKp":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/2_7c80dd9e-4782-47b3-ba9f-67c242eab88f.jpg","media_width":50,"media_position":"start","text_position":"place-self-center-start text-start","icon":"none","icon_width":48,"subheading":"","sub_position":"top","title":"Quiet, Smooth and Precise Lifting","heading_tag":"h3","content":"<p>Designed to seamlessly integrate into the dynamic movement of gamers all day<br\/><\/p><ul><li>&lt;1mm - Positioning error accuracy<\/li><li>&lt;2mm - Cumulative error*<\/li><li>&lt;45dB - Motor operation noise<\/li><li>1\/20 - Precision adjustment<\/li><\/ul>","link_text":"","link_url":"","background":"#ffffff","background_inner":"#ffffff","background_gradient":"","text_color":"#000000","text_gradient":"","button_background":"","button_text_color":"","allow_reverse":false}},"image_QTXNd8":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/10_28fd39ff-dd21-4e36-8382-b12001775875.jpg","media_width":50,"media_position":"end","text_position":"place-self-center-start text-start","icon":"none","icon_width":48,"subheading":"","sub_position":"top","title":"Integrated Control Panel","heading_tag":"h3","content":"<p>One-touch fingertip operation<br\/><\/p><ul><li>4-preset height memory<\/li><li>4-level anti-collision rebound<\/li><li>Sitting reminder<br\/><\/li><\/ul>","link_text":"","link_url":"","background":"#ffffff","background_inner":"#ffffff","background_gradient":"","text_color":"#000000","text_gradient":"","button_background":"","button_text_color":"","allow_reverse":false}},"image_9zJc79":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/3_f84cdd70-485a-4fba-9a59-295e32e6c521.jpg","media_width":50,"media_position":"start","text_position":"place-self-center-start text-start","icon":"none","icon_width":48,"subheading":"","sub_position":"top","title":"Dual-motor High-speed Drive System","heading_tag":"h3","content":"<p>Elevator-like smoothness in lifting engineered for gamers' dynamic lifestyles<br\/><\/p><ul><li>710mm -1170mm - height adjustment range<\/li><li>125kg(275lbs) - Max load capacity<\/li><li>20,000+ - lift cycles supported<br\/><\/li><\/ul>","link_text":"","link_url":"","background":"#ffffff","background_inner":"#ffffff","b